{"tid":1804432,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"睇完返校之後，希望大家唔再逃避呢一切，而且要努力咁活下去。","createTime":"2019-12-31T03:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T16:35:08.000Z","uid":34676,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ea18065e83e05b609d93f332a303207933c4665b","tid":1804432,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:56:52.000Z","msg":"呢件事係由六月九號開始發生<br />\n呢半年就好似一場永遠都唔會醒嘅惡夢咁<br />\n就好似返校入面由死者同負罪所構成嘅世界一樣<br />\n每一步都充滿住未知同迷惘<br />\n半年有過千條浮屍，不計其數嘅被自殺，警渣強姦手足<br />\n以上都係有紀錄嘅報導，冇被報出嚟嘅呢？poly 火車上嘅手足？831 太子不存在嘅cctv呢？<br />\n由梁義士嘅死到周梓樂，加埋種種俾警渣逼害因而發生意外嘅事故<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢半年，大家真係過得好痛苦。最痛苦係自己無能為力，每日都有好多好難受嘅資訊，而正正因為難受咗太耐，所以慢慢就變成逃避。甚至有人萌生自殺嘅念頭。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n唔知幾時開始，打開手機唔敢再上連登，因為見到啲負面標題好似鞭打緊自己咁。<br />\n唔知幾時開始，唔敢再睇新聞，因為怕又傳來噩耗。<br />\n唔知幾時開始，將「下，警察大撚哂架wo」掛喺嘴邊，而心裡又慢慢接受。<br />\n唔知幾時開始，上少咗Twitter，因為怕睇到啲外國議員post 得幾百人like。<br />\n唔知幾時開始，覺得聯署簽名冇用，但其實都只係撳個掣嘅事。<br />\n唔知幾時開始，要靠其他人嘅犧牲去維持自己嘅信念。<br />\n<br />\n上個禮拜我睇完返校，其中有幾句對白我一直都忘記唔到，就好似一巴掌摑醒我咁。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「你是忘記了，還是害怕想起來？」<br />\n「把所有的痛苦都留在過去，就這麼忘了不好嗎？」<br />\n「總得有人活下來，記得這一切得來不易。」</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n雖然每日都好難受，但呢一切又點會可以逃避到，點能夠忘記呢？<br />\n我地唔單止唔可以逃避，仲要好好咁去面對，咁先對得住流過血，受傷過，犧牲咗嘅人。<br />\n<br />\n（題外話：喺到推薦所有人入場睇返校，可以參考返呢個post，唔好去錯戲院睇啊<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1790760/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1790760/page/1</a>）"},{"pid":"ba62bcd921f0b12ac08b49539b7937e81f30bcbc","tid":1804432,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T03:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QVJSfAK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQVJSfAK.jpg&h=1c3a2fe3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1bkAXO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1bkAXO5.jpg&h=250b2755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdsr4t5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcdsr4t5.jpg&h=9fa8fb56&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CMe2CO6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCMe2CO6.jpg&h=6534546d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jn3nCO6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJn3nCO6.jpg&h=64343c19&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ffb0c7315e9c1488b44a401987323599cb8bd7e5","tid":1804432,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:00:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8eede915815c912419c9b9dab37465ae48dfe5e8","tid":1804432,"uid":105114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f203caf757d592403c32b619b19afc964ed0d64","tid":1804432,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-31T04:16:17.000Z","msg":"<ins>德國聯署</ins><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">1. deadline 25/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MHkcG1&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=7357f360\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MHkcG1</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">2. deadline 30/12 (成功) </span> <span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"https://bit.ly/369xL99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F369xL99&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJvY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=28a1a321\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/369xL99</a></span><br />\n<br />\n3. 暫時最後一個 deadline <span style=\"color: orange;\">1/1 </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">仲要24000人 </span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">［附教學］ <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1803675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">h